        LLM (LARGE LANGUAGE MODEL)

This are AI systems trained on vast text data to understand, generate, and summarise human-like language, powering toools like ChatGpt.
Using transformer architecture, they predict the next word in sequence based on patterns.


    KEY LLM USES
        coding assistance 
        content generation 
        translation 
        analysis
        
CAPABILITIES & APPLICATIONS
    Content Generation 
        creating articles 
        reports
        marketing copy 
    Contextual Understanding 
        summarizing long documents 
        identfying trends 
    Coding and debugging
        software development 
        web development 
        bug bounty 
    Interaction 
        chatbots
        virtual assistants 


LLM EXAMPLES 
    GPT (openAI)
    Gemini
    Claude (Anthropic)
    LLama
    Grok (XAI)
    Mistral
    Deepseek

